Aurélien Rigotti is a PhD student working on sea ice rheology as part of WP2. He is supervised by Véronique Dansereau and Jérôme Weiss at the National Center for Scientific Research in Grenoble, France.
&quot; I hope my work will play its part and continue to be discussed, criticized, and explored. Véronique, Jérôme, and I are contributing to a promising path for the rheology community..&quot;
An interview with Aurélien Rigotti.
